:{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33879,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/06\/prophet-angered-by-triple-talaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":25058,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Divorce: The Prophet is angered by triple talaq","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Mahmud ibn Labid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was informed about a man who pronounced divorce to his wife three times at once. The Prophet stood in anger and he said, \u201cDo they play with the Book of Allah while I am among you?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2981,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/20\/allah-loves-strong-weak-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":25058,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Allah loves strong believers, but all good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe strong believer is more beloved to Allah than the weak believer, but there is goodness in both of them. Be eager for what benefits you, seek help from Allah, and do not be frustrated. If\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37406,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/22\/islamic-knowledge-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":25058,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on \u2018Ilm: Islamic knowledge not for worldly gain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not acquire knowledge to impress the scholars, nor to argue with the fools, and do not seek the best seat in the gatherings through it. Whoever does so, then to the Hellfire, to the Hellfire!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7283,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/prophets-righteous-severely-tested\/","url_meta":{"origin":25058,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Trials: The Prophets, righteous most severely tested","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa'd ibn Abi Waqqas reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which people are tested most severely?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThey are the prophets, then the next best, then the next best. A man is put to trial according to his religion.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/why-servants-despair\/","url_meta":{"origin":25058,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Laughter: Why make My servants despair?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to a group of his companions while they were laughing and talking. The Prophet said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, if you knew what I knew, you would laugh little and weep often.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25058","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25058"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25058\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=25058"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=25058"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=25058"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}